    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The procedure of marking or coloring the skin by pricking in coloring matter so as to form indelible marks as figures or by production of scars.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
